# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok former president p.w. botha will continue defying a commission investigating apartheid-era human rights abuses , even though he faces criminal prosecution for doing so , a newspaper reported thursday .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (n / newspaper)
      :ARG1 (c / continue-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "P.W."
                        :op2 "Botha")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president)
                        :time (f / former)))
            :ARG1 (d / defy-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (c2 / commission
                        :ARG0-of (ii / investigate-01
                              :ARG1 (a / abuse-01
                                    :ARG1 (r2 / right-05
                                          :ARG1 (h2 / human))
                                    :time (e / era
                                          :mod (a2 / apartheid))))))
            :concession (f2 / face-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p3 / prosecute-01
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG2 d
                        :ARG2-of (c3 / criminal-03))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok on a near party-line vote of ##-## , the republican-controlled senate on wednesday approved an $ ##.# billion spending bill for veterans and housing programs that eliminates one of president clinton 's major initiatives , the national service program known as americorps .
# ::alignments
(a / approve-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Senate")
            :ARG1-of (c / control-01
                  :ARG0 (p / political-party
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Republican"))))
      :ARG1 (b / bill
            :ARG3-of (s / spend-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (v / veteran)
                        :op2 (p2 / program
                              :mod (h / house-01))))
            :ARG0-of (e / eliminate-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / program
                        :quant 1
                        :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                              :ARG2 (ii2 / initiative
                                    :poss (p4 / person
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Clinton")
                                          :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                                :ARG2 (p5 / president)))
                                    :ARG1-of (m / major-02))
                              :domain (p6 / program
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "America")
                                    :mod (s2 / service
                                          :mod (n5 / nation))
                                    :ARG1-of (k / know-02
                                          :ARG2 (m2 / military
                                                :name (n6 / name
                                                      :op1 "National"
                                                      :op2 "Service"))))))))
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :manner (v2 / vote-01
            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (a3 / amr-unintelligible
                  :value "-##")
            :mod (l / line
                  :mod (p7 / party))
            :ARG1-of (n7 / near-02)))

            :name (n2 / name

                              :ARG1 p
                              :ARG2 (h4 / husband)))

                        :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 2
                              :unit (m2 / month)))))

                  :op1 "Santiago"))

                        :op1 "Muslim")))

            :unit (m / month))

                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91

                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :month 1
                        :time-of j)))
      :weekday (m2 / monday))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok after months of rumors and a week of protests , the french government has finally confirmed that in exchange for a sum said to be $ ### million to $ # billion , it will rent the name , art treasures and expertise of the louvre to a new museum to be built in abu dhabi , the capital of the united arab emirates .

                  :ARG1 (c2 / country

                              :op1 "France"))))

            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (n2 / name)
                  :op2 (t / treasure
                        :mod (a2 / art))
                  :op3 (e / expertise
                        :poss (l / louvre)))
            :ARG3 (m / museum
                  :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)
                  :ARG1-of (b / build-01
                        :location (c3 / city
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Abu"
                                    :op2 "Dhabi")
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (e2 / emirate
                                          :ARG1-of (u / unite-01)
                                          :location c2
                                          :name (n5 / name
                                                :op1 "Iraq")))
                              :ARG2 (c4 / capital)))))
      :ARG1-of (e3 / exchange-01
            :ARG3 (s / sum
                  :ARG1-of (s2 / say-01
                        :ARG3 (b2 / between
                              :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                                    :quant 1000000000
                                    :unit (d / dollar))
                              :op2 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                                    :quant 1000000000
                                    :unit (d2 / dollar))))))
      :time (f / final)
      :time (a3 / after
            :op1 (a4 / and

                        :quant 1
                        :unit (m4 / month)))))

                  :mod (e / exact))
            :domain p))

                                          :op1 "Tanzania"))))

      :ARG0 (t / tally-01
            :ARG1-of (r / release-01
                  :ARG0 (r2 / research-institute
                        :topic (t2 / technology
                              :mod (ii / industry)))
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (m / monday))))
      :ARG1 (r3 / reach-01
            :ARG0 (v / value
                  :ARG2-of (p / produce-01
                        :ARG0 ii
                        :mod (e / electricity)
                        :mod (m2 / mechanics))))
      :ARG1 (m3 / monetary-quantity
            :quant 1000000000
            :unit (d2 / dollar)))

                        :ARG1-of (m / marred-01
                              :ARG0 (c3 / charge-05
                                    :ARG2 (p4 / politics
                                          :ARG1-of (d2 / dirty-02))
                                    :time (m2 / minute
                                          :mod (l / last)))))
                  :direction (p5 / past
                        :op1 p3)))
      :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
            :ARG2 (s3 / senator)))

# ::id 1953 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok australia 's #### national rugby league season will remain at ## weeks as clubs can not afford to play a shorter season , despite <unk> 's a big drop in revenue for them .
# ::alignments
(r / remain-01
      :ARG1 (s / season
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Australia"))
            :mod (l / league
                  :name n
                  :op1 "Rugby")
            :mod (n2 / nation))
      :ARG3 (m / multiple
            :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (w / week)))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (p / possible-01
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG1 (a / afford-01
                        :ARG0 (c3 / club)
                        :ARG1 (p2 / play-01
                              :ARG0 c3
                              :ARG1 (s2 / season
                                    :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG2 (s3 / short-07
                                                :ARG1 s2)
                                          :ARG3 (m2 / more)))))
                  :concession (d / drop-01
                        :ARG1 (r2 / revenue)
                        :ARG2 c3
                        :mod (b / big)))))

            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "New"
                  :op2 "Lealand"))

                  :ARG1 (t / trade-01)
                  :ARG2 (e2 / economy)))
      :subevent-of (t2 / talk-01
            :ARG0 (a2 / and

                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Hu"
                              :op2 "Jintao")

                              :ARG1 c
                              :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
                  :op2 (p3 / person
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Helen"
                              :op2 "Clark")
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 c
                              :ARG2 (m / minister
                                    :mod (p4 / prime)))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))))

                                    :op1 "China"))))

                  :ARG2 (a / advanced-02
                        :ARG1 p)
                  :ARG3 (m2 / most)))

            :ARG1 p)

      :location (h3 / here))

# ::id 1957 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok nigerian stocks buoyed by high demand for shares rose this week by four percent , with the all-share index moving from last week 's level of ##,###.## points to ##,###.## points , brokers said friday .
# ::alignments
(m / multi-sentence
      :snt1 (r / rise-01
            :ARG0 (d / demand-01
                  :ARG1 (s / share)
                  :ARG1-of (h / high-02))
            :ARG1 (s2 / stock
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Niger")))
            :ARG2 (p / percentage-entity
                  :value 4)
            :time (w / week
                  :mod (t / this)))
      :snt2 (m2 / move-01
            :ARG1 (ii / index
                  :mod (s3 / share
                        :mod (a / all)))
            :ARG2 (l / level
                  :poss (w2 / week
                        :mod (l2 / last))
                  :mod (s4 / string-entity
                        :value "http://.christianforums.com"))
            :source (p2 / point-04
                  :mod s4
                  :value "http://"))
      :snt3 (s5 / say-01
            :ARG0 (p3 / person
                  :ARG0-of (b / broker-01))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (f / friday))))
